Written evidence from Scope (LTC 37)[bold]&#xa0;[bold]About Scope[bold]We all want to live in a world of opportunity – to be able to live our own life, play our part and be valued for the person we are. At Scope we’re passionate about possibility.
[normal] 
[normal]It inspires us every day and means we never set limits on people’s potential.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]We work with disabled people and their families at every stage of their lives.
[normal] 
[normal]From offering day to day support and information, to challenging assumptions about disability and influencing decision makers – everything we do is about creating real and lasting change.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]We believe that a world where all disabled people have the same opportunities as everyone else would be a pretty incredible place for all of us. Together we can make it happen. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Scope welcomes the opportunity to submit evidence to this Inquiry. 
[normal]&#xa0;
